{"tid":1309414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登網民再發起眾籌　英國報章刊全版廣告　籲關注「中共違中英聯合聲明」","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T07:45:52.000Z","uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"299ae6d317c7bf39b9550a59e0b90d245f53fa46","tid":1309414,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:45:52.000Z","msg":"有網民早前在 G20峰會前夕發起眾籌，於全球登報「反送中」，有連登網民今日再發起眾籌，打算透過反覆刊登英國報章全版、持續網絡攻勢，令英國政府、大眾認真看待中國違反《中英聯合聲明》，「繼而（英國）推出措施支援香港人，協助我哋反守為攻！」<br />\n他們目標眾籌（眾籌網站）約30萬英鎊（約 294 萬港元），網民今早在連登「開 post」一小時後，已籌得 6 萬英鎊 （58萬）。<br />\n連登論壇用家「我要攬炒」今日在連登公布眾籌計劃，他提到已經兩日內設計了十多款登報文案，標題提到 1984 年簽署的中英聯合聲明，有關聲明決定香港人前途。<br />\n<br />\n網民指出，希望透過聲明，「令英國政府、大眾認真看待中共違反《中英聯合聲明》，繼而推出措施支援香港人，協助我哋反守為攻！」<br />\n網民指出，為了確保是次眾籌公開公正，眾籌將會有專業會計師及律師監察，如果最後有餘額，將全數捐贈俾英國非牟利組織 Hong Kong Watch。Hong Kong Watch 由一班英國政壇關心香港人士自發組成，一直有與英國國會議員聯繫，關注《中英聯合聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E5%88%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E7%B1%B2%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%81%95%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E5%2588%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=31683f93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E5%2588%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%2F&h=03d47604\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E5%88%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E7%B1%B2%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%81%95%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E/</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔號召力仲勁過陳方安生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}